               stealing, on the <rs id="t18181028-60-cd349" type="crimeDate">8th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18181028-60-off348 t18181028-60-cd349"></join>, three pounds of gold solder, value 4s.; 19 gold links, value 4s., and two pennyweights of gold, value 6s.
            </rs>, the property of 
               <persName id="t18181028-60-victim456" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
